title: Roy Hodgson to shuffle his England pack in Lithuania - Stalbans Review
text:
England boss Roy Hodgson plans to assess his options in Lithuania after releasing five players from the squad for next week's trip to Vilnius. Hodgson announced after Friday night's 2-0 win over Estonia - a ninth successive Euro 2016 qualifying win - that he will give senior figures a rest.
 Stalbans Review.
